Mark Kiely https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mark_Kiely 0 Mark Kiely is an American actor, probably best known for his recurring guest appearance as Gil Meyers in Beverly Hills, 90210. He also appeared in Charlie's Angels and "The Judge." He currently lives in Rhode Island and is a beloved swim coach to many. He also graduated from Assumption College in Worcester, Mass.
